<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-6478] TestNG test cases not working correctly with groups</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6478</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the Camel TestNG integration, tests work fine when no -groups are specified, but fail if a group is selected. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is due to the default behavior of TestNG&apos;s annotations. @BeforeClass, @AfterClass, etc need a &quot;alwaysRun = true&quot; argument in order to still run when groups are selected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is really a peculiarity in the way TestNG works, but nonetheless, the Camel support classes do not work with TestNG groups&lt;/p&gt;</description>
